    <div class="c-recipe__item c-recipe__description">
          <p>Plum tomatoes, ketchup, molasses and soy sauce come together to create a succulent sauce for simmering pork shoulder. Once the meat is in the slow cooker, just wait and enjoy the lovely smell wafting through the house. Once cooked, the pork is shredded and ready to garnish a mouth-watering burger.</p>
        </div>
